Ways to reduce water depletion, protect water quality, and support healthy ecosystems:

Donations:
- https://www.embracerelief.org/the-hidden-thirst-of-technology-how-ai-is-consuming-millions-of-gallons-of-water/
- https://ai4good.org/
- https://theconservationfoundation.org/ai-for-conservation/
- https://www.foodandwaterwatch.org/2025/10/06/lfl-ai-data-center-boom-water-climate/

Personal:
- took a shorter shower
- turned off water when brushing teeth or washing hands/face
- ran a full load in the dishwasher or washing machine
- fixed a leak
- scraped dishes instead of rinsing before loading the dishwasher
- other: user input

Learn:
- https://lakeconews.com/news/82566-ai-has-a-hidden-water-cost-heres-how-to-calculate-yours
- https://www.eesi.org/articles/view/data-centers-and-water-consumption
- https://oecd.ai/en/wonk/how-much-water-does-ai-consume
- https://www.businessenergyuk.com/knowledge-hub/chatgpt-energy-consumption-visualized/
